{"tid":172471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佔中發起人<戴耀廷>表示 將投票予 曾俊華","createTime":"2017-03-26T02:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T02:35:17.000Z","uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b38fb47d26e24e3cf5975c70c8bcf2f20e487cd","tid":172471,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T02:33:17.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】高等教育界選委戴耀廷表示，他和所有高教界選委均會投票予曾俊華，預計曾俊華可以得三百多票。他指自己是根據民間投票的結果投票，又指選舉策略不能只考慮政綱原則。<br />\n<br />\n立法會主席梁君彥表示，投票意向與經民聯一致，沒有回應是否投票給林鄭月娥。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=215461\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D215461&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0CvnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=f67d5d27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D215461&h=cdeb69dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=215461</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2014/09/1409241818472147.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F09%2F1409241818472147.jpg&h=07541d92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20150510/s00046/1431250456957_59ABB03CBFA936EC167DEA8DCCD0C720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20150510%2Fs00046%2F1431250456957_59ABB03CBFA936EC167DEA8DCCD0C720.jpg&h=1b584607&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/726923/726923_20140620-101914.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2F726923%2F726923_20140620-101914.png&h=117fac8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc2696e297b53bd00da21f708284cdf3e46ce217","tid":172471,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]